      • buildVisualGraph

        public VisualGraph buildVisualGraph​(AstNode node,
                                    boolean decorate)
        Builds a VisualGraph representing the provided AST node. The graph can then be exported using a GraphBuilder like DotBuilder.
        Parameters:
        node - An AST node representing the root of the tree to be generated
        decorate - Whether to include references to the declaration of various identifiers (requires context analysis to be done)
        Returns:
        The generated VisualGraph
